Welcome to RoninMUD.

We are a fantastic mud with many great custom areas and
many friendly players.  Take your time, look around
and see what we have to offer.

We suggest you start with typing "HELP HIGHLIGHTS" and
"HELP INTRODUCTION". These give a nice summary of our world.

Our homepage is
  http://www.roninmud.org

If you are in trouble, type "home", this will work ONLY until
you reach level 10.

Welcome and Enjoy!
   
   